未充分考虑礼物的性质和价值。而王某仙作为园长，或许也应更加谨慎地对待学生的礼物，避免引起不必要的争议。这一案件提醒着教育工作者，在严格遵守教育部规定的同时，也要正确处理与学生和家长的关系，避免因小失大。同时，幼儿园在执行规定时，也应更加理性和审慎，给予员工合理的解释和改正机会，共同营造良好的教育环境。重庆一园长因收学生6.16元巧克力被开除，法院：不宜定性为收受礼品，幼儿园违法解除劳动合同应赔偿_腾讯新闻"},"attached_info":"CkAIsLfX6M/K8dtPEAMaCTExMDI0OTM3OSDM0s62BjAAOMEBQARyCTY2NTg3MjA0N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"281 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-da7c1b7c767074cf54f721449ed14a4f_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1725194463.562424","card_id":"Q_665281234","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":665281234,"title":"如何评价2024年第38届中国化学奥林匹克竞赛（初赛）?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665281234","type":"question","created":1724593897,"answer_count":39,"follower_count":83,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4217,16253,38083,115936,313684],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"举办时间：2024年9月1日"},"attached_info":"Cj8IsLfX6M/K8dtPEAMaCTExMDExNzg2NSDp7ay2BjAAOFNABXIJNjY1MjgxMjM0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"107 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-b4a3021c87e81302433ce2156cf8da56_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1725194463.563485","card_id":"Q_661221458","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":661221458,"title":"黄权为什么没有偷偷逃回蜀国？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/661221458","type":"question","created":1720584404,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":53,"author"